name: YoOoNGZ #44
description:
☆ ☆ They are not what you think they are.


Portuguese guys usually don’t like Brazilian guys…

One of my friends spilled a drink on a girl and quickly apologized. The dudes of her group suddenly started a fight with us. Out of nowhere

Took some punches, kicked some butts and a face. And went away.

The first fight of my life. In Portugal.
